channel.description:
Evidently my Soul Split is sending the projectiles, and is healing/smiting
endlessly until i stop attacking.
is there any way to create a delay?

Here's an example of my code:
[code]
    public static void handleSoulSplit(final Player p, final NPC n, int dmg) {
        if (p.Soulsplit == true) {
            int gain = (dmg / 2);
            p.getSkills().heal(gain);
            World.getWorld().getProjectileManager().fire(p.getLocation(), n.getLocation(), 50, 70, 2263, 11, 11, n);
            World.getWorld().registerEvent(new Event(600) {

                @Override
                public void execute() {
                    n.graphics(2264);
                    this.stop();
                }
